_json.gridTitle: How to Repair Plastic Bumper Scratches
_json.description: Is your car bumper scuffed or scratched? While not as severe as a crack or dent a trip to a repair shop not only costs quite a bit, but they will probably need to keep your car for a day or two. So why not fix it yourself? In this instructable we are going to show you how to repair a scratched plastic or fiberglass bumper cover on your own, in a fraction of the time, and at a fraction of the cost.
